{"tid":1866803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年2月7日 — 早晨，Twitter戰線須要大家","createTime":"2020-02-07T01:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T15:58:48.000Z","uid":253983,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4e4669001456224d837478f801fd25f952e616ff","tid":1866803,"uid":253983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:59:41.000Z","msg":"醫護手足無放棄過我地，我地都唔好放棄，好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n做我地能夠做到嘢啦，例如Twitter戰線<br />\n<br />\n呢度有個今日任務嘅匯集，大家可以㩒呢條link入今日嘅任務<br />\n記得 Like + Retweet <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原Tweet</span></span> 呀 <br />\n(總係有朋友仔Like + Tweet我地個comment就算，係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">㩒入去原Tweet先Like + Retweet</span></span>呀)<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tweetingforhk/status/1225590519553810432?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftweetingforhk%2Fstatus%2F1225590519553810432%3Fs%3D21&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=a80b2b7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftweetingforhk%2Fstatus%2F1225590519553810432%3Fs%3D21&h=76a84055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tweetingforhk/status/1225590519553810432?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n另外歡迎大家follow呢個Twitter，留意每日Twitter戰線任務<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTweetingforHK&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=330f9da9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK</a>"},{"pid":"e60441daab37ec8a660b8886909bd3fdff7fce8a","tid":1866803,"uid":253983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:06:40.000Z","msg":"推 1/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cb94c3fce1bb3d30adcea1af2fa3d25807b15e","tid":1866803,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:06:56.000Z","msg":"唔想再有手足被黑警自殺？用呢4個a